`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The `[role]` directory uses literal square brackets (Next.js dynamic segment), which causes glob tools to misinterpret it as a character class pattern — that's why `Glob` reported "no files found" even though `find` located the file correctly. Always fall back to `Bash`/`find` when globbing paths with bracket segments.
